":38923,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/28\/visualizing-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35883,"position":3},"title":"Sa\u2019id on Salah: Visualizing the Day of Resurrection in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Abdur Rahman reported: I said to Sa\u2019id ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cO Abu Muhammad, what is this weeping that confronts you in your prayer?\u201d Sa\u2019id said, \u201cO nephew, why do you ask about it?\u201d He said, \u201cO uncle, perhaps Allah will benefit me.\u201d Sa\u2019id\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37332,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/07\/never-die-twice\/","url_meta":{"origin":35883,"position":4},"title":"Abu Bakr on Muhammad: The Prophet will never die twice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 7, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Abu Bakr came riding on his horse from his dwelling in al-Sunuh until he arrived and entered the mosque. He did not speak to people until he entered the home of Aisha while the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was covered with a shroud.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38549,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/25\/tahajjud-awf\/","url_meta":{"origin":35883,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tahajjud: Aw